import Vue from 'vue'
import Router from 'vue-router'
import Login from './views/Login.vue'
import Main from './views/Main.vue'
import NotFound from './views/NotFound.vue'
import Plist from './views/ProductList.vue'
import Padd from './views/ProductAdd.vue'
import Stat from './views/Stat.vue'
import Uadd from './views/UserAdd.vue'
import Ulist from './views/UserList.vue'

Vue.use(Router)

export default new Router({
    routes: [
        {path: '/',name: 'login',component: Login},
        {path: '/login',name: 'login',component: Login},
        {path: '/main',name: 'main',component: Main,children: [
                {path: '',name: 'stat',component: Stat},
                {path: 'stat',name: 'stat',component: Stat},
                {path: 'plist',name: 'plist',component: Plist},
                {path: 'padd',name: 'padd',component: Padd},
                {path: 'ulist',name: 'ulist',component: Ulist},
                {path: 'uadd',name: 'uadd',component: Uadd}
            ]},
        {path: '/*',name: 'notfound',component: NotFound}
    ]
})
